	<tr><td colspan="2" bgcolor="#666699" vAlign="TOP">
	<p><font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="2" color="#FFFFFF"><font color="skyblue">My recommendation would be to do adventures (I'm presuming you have LDoN).  I have yet to be in a group that objects to someone being the MLer.  This person loots all corpses, sells vendor trash, etc.  After the adventure is done, they sell the vendor trash and split all the cash loot.  I have averaged around 70pp per adventure.  I think it's safe to say that the average time to complete an adventure is around an hour.  Compared to an average of 150pp for your 3 to 4 hours, it's a better deal in both XP and loot.<br />
<br />
The other thing you could do is duo HGs in Rathe Mountains, or seafury cyclopses in Ocean of Tears.</font></font></p>
	
	<p><p><img src="/forums/images/sig_separator.gif" width="282" height="11" Alt="Hey! Watch where you point that thing!"><br>
