	<tr><td colspan="2" bgcolor="#666699" vAlign="TOP">
	<p><font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="2" color="#FFFFFF">You guys really all use autosplit`?<br />
I have been on Kael Drakkal for about 1 year now. With my mage or cleric I NEVER had a group that autosplits the cash. Always had a MainLooter assigned who split all the money in the end. I know that this method could be manipulated by the main looter, but in all the pick up groups I was in it seemed fair.<br />
<br />
Only one time, when my mage was in her 30is I did a round of geos in CC. Did the whole thing for about 4 hours and a lot of gems dropped. When we called it a day the looter when LD and was never to be seen again.<br />
Since it only happend once to me I am still very happy on how this method works.</font></p>
	
